{"tid":1753214,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"而家開始多多參與自己選區既活動／事務！！！","createTime":"2019-11-25T01:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:35:44.000Z","uid":172599,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3f849f831cea828d2e16d4843b36db46ccd1b5","tid":1753214,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:52:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;我成日提醒自己，政治既工作係爭取不同意見既人既支持&quot; - 梁天琦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔係佢fans，但都好同意佢講既野<br />\n今日既結果，大家都好意外，驚喜又開心，開心下係幾好既！<br />\n既然我地有個咁好既outcome, 咁梗係要用盡佢黎打立法會啦～<br />\n點打？<br />\n有人話，而家都係６：４比，情況仍然唔太樂觀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁好簡單啫！　爭取更大比率咪得囉！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你以為得你當區區議員可以幫到手？唔係！作為居民既你，你都有可以做既野架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">１）由而家開始，做個好鄰居</span></span><br />\n可能你好憎藍絲，好憎廢老，ｔｈａｔｓ　ｏｋａｙ.<br />\n但由今日開始，我希望你睇佢地係持票者，而佢地既支持同一票係十分之關鍵。<br />\n試諗下，就算佢果區既區議員，都只係一日見佢７&mdash;８個鐘，之後佢都要放工。但係既隔離鄰舍係２４小時都係你隔離。所以，由今日開始請你好好打個招呼，煮多左野就請佢地食，請佢地仔女食，讓佢地知道你係一個好人。當然有時間就了解下佢地既政見同參與度啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">２）間唔中參加下你果區區議員既義工活動</span></span><br />\n你既幫手可讓區議員更有動員力，發生咩事既時候居民就更覺得你地成個班底係幫到手，從而就更會對你地所屬既政治團體更有好感。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">３）有錢出錢</span></span><br />\n區議員搞活動／要動員係需要錢，所以請有錢就出錢。<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多方法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45211ac6563171d1bb15bbf7726bbc6af3ec3ce","tid":1753214,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"68bccbd2fe1f82467069c8cbbc59eb8cfa9063f1","tid":1753214,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:53:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6aa61516b3f641eb8d3f3b7f3850abb624d6d02","tid":1753214,"uid":72633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:56:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f1fba448772e90be77a47061fb2556a6621d69a","tid":1753214,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:59:25.000Z","msg":"1/100"},{"pid":"2440329da2729ac46dbb4eedc1e5da66636c3317","tid":1753214,"uid":317094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"建議留番蛇齋餅粽, 以長線connect 長者, 再加實務"},{"pid":"cd9b1df4175d68686976935a580493292494d328","tid":1753214,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2440329da2729ac46dbb4eedc1e5da66636c3317","tid":1753214,"uid":317094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"建議留番蛇齋餅粽, 以長線connect 長者, 再加實務"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"搞下d一天本地遊已經好吸引"},{"pid":"88b3a6d362d91f3181962420969614864b41dbd5","tid":1753214,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"2/100"},{"pid":"ec1d35dce66db80559e0577b38e695b9d2be2cf9","tid":1753214,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:16:13.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"8be49c03e63aad82306542e7eda464bfab6b974a","tid":1753214,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"5/100"},{"pid":"402a74dd988b446d500b9756c94ae242922e30c3","tid":1753214,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"6/100"}]}